@startuml Battle Phase — State Machine

skinparam StateFontSize 13
skinparam ArrowFontSize 11

[*] --> Placement : BattleMode.Enter

Placement --> TurnIdle : OnPlacementConfirmed

TurnIdle --> PlayerTurn : OnUnitReady [player unit]
TurnIdle --> EnemyTurn  : OnUnitReady [enemy unit]

PlayerTurn --> ResolveAction : OnActionChosen
EnemyTurn  --> ResolveAction : OnActionChosen

ResolveAction --> TurnIdle  : OnResolved [battle ongoing]
ResolveAction --> Result    : OnResolved [battle over]

Result --> [*] : OnResultAcknowledged

@enduml
